Source: https://src.fedoraproject.org/rpms/libgda5/blob/f43/f/libgda5-configure-c99.patch

Avoid calling the undeclared printf function in configure checks
by including <stdio.h>.  Implicit function declarations have been
removed from the C language in 1999.

No need to upstream this because upstream has switched to Meson.

